x4freetext: Data were compiled at the Russia MSU SINP
The evaluation procedure was based on the comparison
in detail 206,207Pb data obtained only at Livermore
(USA) with 208Pb data obtained at Livermore, Saclay
(France) and also in other experiments, as well as
with data calculated in the model (CPNRM).
was obtained as SIG-EXP(g,xn) multiplied by 1.13
basing on comparison of SIG-EXP and SIG-THEOR.
